No. 10-10255. Monty Marcellus Shelton, Petitioner v. United States. 563 U.S. 1029, 131 S. Ct. 2946,

180 L. Ed. 2d 239,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 4031. May 31, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied.
